fields.description:
1. Install and run Animation on an iOS device 
2. Select timob_5166 in Acceptance tab 
3. Click on ANIMATION - [WARN] 
4. Click or drag the circle for around 10-15 times
5. Check Expected 
App crashes with following logs, which is not in expected behaviour.
